description: Here it is, eh! 1021 songs played on the best damn radio station in the world, during its best days-the 70's&80's! What a ride, from the early Brampton days! Cutoff is '89, when I moved to Sweden. Had Spotify since 2006, seeing rights come & go, not the least Blue Peter's. Check out The 102.1 Band!
